org.tmt.tcs.pk.wrapper

Class TpkWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tmt.tcs.pk.wrapper.TpkWrapper

  • public class TpkWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a wrapper class for TPK and will act as an endpoint. It helps in calling TPK New Target and Offset methods so that specific demands can be generated by TPK System
